<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Common EJS Errors</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Common EJS Errors</h1>
    <a href="/">Back to Home</a>
  </header>
  
  <main>
    <h2>1. Missing Closing Tag</h2>
    
    <div class="example">
      <h3>Incorrect:</h3>
      <pre><code>&lt;%- include('partials/header') // Missing %&gt;</code></pre>
      
      <h3>Correct:</h3>
      <pre><code>&lt;%- include('partials/header') %&gt;</code></pre>
    </div>
    
    <h2>2. Unclosed Conditional Block</h2>
    
    <div class="example">
      <h3>Incorrect:</h3>
      <pre><code>&lt;% if (user) { %&gt;
  &lt;h2&gt;&lt;%= user.name %&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;% // Missing closing brace and %&gt;</code></pre>
      
      <h3>Correct:</h3>
      <pre><code>&lt;% if (user) { %&gt;
  &lt;h2&gt;&lt;%= user.name %&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;% } %&gt;</code></pre>
    </div>
    
    <h2>3. Incomplete Output Tag</h2>
    
    <div class="example">
      <h3>Incorrect:</h3>
      <pre><code>&lt;h2&gt;&lt;%= user.name // Missing %&gt;</code></pre>
      
      <h3>Correct:</h3>
      <pre><code>&lt;h2&gt;&lt;%= user.name %&gt;</code></pre>
    </div>
    
    <h2>4. Incorrect Include Syntax</h2>
    
    <div class="example">
      <h3>Incorrect:</h3>
      <pre><code>&lt;%- include partials/header %&gt; // Missing parentheses</code></pre>
      
      <h3>Correct:</h3>
      <pre><code>&lt;%- include('partials/header') %&gt;</code></pre>
    </div>
    
    <h2>5. Mixing JavaScript and HTML Without Proper Tags</h2>
    
    <div class="example">
      <h3>Incorrect:</h3>
      <pre><code>&lt;% for(let i=0; i&lt;items.length; i++) {
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;%= items[i] %&gt;&lt;/li&gt; // HTML inside &lt;% %&gt; block
} %&gt;</code></pre>
      
      <h3>Correct:</h3>
      <pre><code>&lt;% for(let i=0; i&lt;items.length; i++) { %&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;%= items[i] %&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;% } %&gt;</code></pre>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <footer>
    <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Express EJS App</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>